      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">02 · Ads</div>
        <div class="service-name">Paid Advertising</div>
        <div class="service-price">Setup from $400 · Mgmt from $500/mo</div>
        <div class="service-desc">Google & Social campaigns built to perform. Strategy, setup, and ongoing management for maximum ROI.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">03 · Funnel</div>
        <div class="service-name">Funnel & Conversion</div>
        <div class="service-price">From $300 CAD</div>
        <div class="service-desc">Landing page optimization and full funnel setup designed to turn traffic into loyal customers.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">04 · Email</div>
        <div class="service-name">Email Marketing</div>
        <div class="service-price">Setup from $300 · Mgmt from $300/mo</div>
        <div class="service-desc">Automated email flows and monthly campaigns that nurture leads and drive repeat revenue.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">05 · Creative</div>
        <div class="service-name">Creative Services</div>
        <div class="service-price">From $200 CAD</div>
        <div class="service-desc">Ad creatives — images and video — plus catalog and brochure design that elevates your brand presence.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card" style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:center; align-items:center; text-align:center; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201,168,76,0.06), var(--dark3));">
        <div style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-size:22px; color:var(--white); margin-bottom:12px;">Ready to grow?</div>
        <div style="font-size:11px; color:var(--white-dim); margin-bottom:28px; line-height:1.7;">Let's build something extraordinary together.</div>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline">Get in Touch</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PACKAGES -->
<section>
  <div id="packages" class="reveal" style="max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p class="section-label">Investment</p>
